sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Browser
    participant Server

    User->>Browser: Fills form and clicks "Save"
    Note right of Browser: Event handler intercepts form submission (preventDefault)
    Browser->>Browser: Create new note object (content, date)
    Browser->>Browser: Add note to local notes array
    Browser->>Browser: Rerender notes list on page
    Browser->>Server: POST /new_note_spa (JSON: content, date)
    Server-->>Browser: 201 Created (no redirect)
    Note right of Browser: Page does not reload; new note appears immediately
